reasons.long = c("NON-WOTUS - Intrastate stream that does not connect to a paragraph (a)(1) or (a)(2) water",
"NON-WOTUS - Intrastate lake or pond not identified in paragraphs (a)(1 - 4) that is not relatively permanent or does not have a continuous surface connection to (a)(1) or (3) water",
"NON-WOTUS - Wetland that does not have a continuous surface connection to a paragraph (a)(1) water or to a relatively permanent paragraph (a)(2) impoundment or paragraph (a)(3) tributary",
"NON-WOTUS - Tributary evaluated under (a)(3) and determined to not be a relatively permanent water with a continuous surface connection to paragraph (a)(1) or (a)(3) water",
"(a)(1)(i) Traditional Navigable Water, also subject to Sections 9 or 10 of the Rivers and Harbors Act (Section 10/404)",
"(a)(2) Jurisdictional Impoundment (Section 404 Only)",
"(a)(3) Tributary (Section 404 Only)",
"(a)(4)(ii) Adjacent Wetland, adjacent to a relatively permanent paragraph (a)(2) Impoundment or (a)(3) Tributary (Section 404 Only)",
"(a)(4)(i) Adjacent Wetland, adjacent to (a)(1)(i) TNW",
"(a)(5) Intrastate Lake or Pond not Identified in Paragraphs (a)(1) through (4), that is a relatively permanent, standing or continuously flowing body of water (Section 404 Only)",
"(b)(5) Artificial lakes or ponds created in dry land, used exclusively for specific purposes (Excluded)",
"(b)(1) Waste Treatment System (Excluded)",
"(b)(4) Artificially irrigated areas that would revert to dry land if the irrigation ceased (Excluded)",
